rComments: Fair professor, he tries to make the class understand and he takes time to answer questions and is very polite + helpful.  After all, this IS organic chem which is hard on it's own, but he tries to help you understand.  Exams reflect class material and assignments.  Textbook chapters that he gives are handy if you need more practice or examples.

He was a really good prof, his lectures were very clear, and he made the course seem fairly easy. Midterms were fair, but when the exam rolled around, most of the course did terrible. His exams are long, hard and out of context to the level you would think from attending his lectures. Overall good prof, but disappointing final exam.
Very good prof! midterms r fare but exam was quite long!
